THIRD-PARTY ACKNOWLEDGEMENTS
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

ARKLinux builds upon the following upstream projects (non-exhaustive):

  • Arch Linux          — https://archlinux.org/              (GPL variants)
  • Linux Kernel        — https://kernel.org/                 (GPL-2.0-only)
  • systemd             — https://systemd.io/                 (LGPL-2.1)
  • nftables            — https://netfilter.org/projects/nftables/ (GPL-2.0)
  • GRUB 2              — https://www.gnu.org/software/grub/  (GPL-3.0)
  • Python              — https://python.org/                 (PSF-2.0)
  • mkinitcpio          — https://archlinux.org/              (GPL-2.0)
  • archiso             — https://archlinux.org/              (GPL-3.0)
  • Btrfs               — https://btrfs.readthedocs.io/       (GPL-2.0)
  • cosign / sigstore   — https://sigstore.dev/               (Apache-2.0)
  • Syft (SBOM)         — https://github.com/anchore/syft     (Apache-2.0)

Full SBOM is available in the GitHub Release assets for each release tag.

